<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Landing Page</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; }
      to { opacity: 1; }
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background-color:#6e0d76;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .jumbotron {
      background-image: url('https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/zTN8-iXKrxJpI824Q9fcmLe6mPEljLGTxlkqY9loje8XlUTCaMa5VQPqoD0x4Puq-3U-qnP8zBgEOK0o-s9v8zTfp64ehij8a3GGsS-mdYwhkqBCVvuiRLh2aAi6U7c0uA=w1280');
      background-size: 100% 100%;
      width:100%;
      height: 600px;
      text-align: center;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      align-items: center;
      vertical-align: top;
      color: #fff;
      animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
    }
    .jumbotron h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 0 20px 50px 20px;
    }
    .jumbotron p {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin: 0 20px 50px 20px;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background-color: #21b92b;
      border-color: #21b92b;
      width: 50%;
      align-self: center;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: rgba(18, 209, 230, 0.874) ;
      border-color: rgba(18, 209, 230, 0.874)  ;
      animation: buttonHover 0.3s ease forwards;
    }
    .btn-primary:active {
      background-color: rgba(18, 228, 251, 0.874) !important;
      border-color: rgba(18, 228, 251, 0.874) !important;
    }
    .custom-bg-purple2 {
	background-color: hsl(299, 93%, 20%);
}
@keyframes buttonHover {
  0% {
    transform: scale(1);
  }
  50% {
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }
  100% {
    transform: scale(1);
  }
}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="jumbotron">
    <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/BQ6tACmgRMwmshe0548ghMgf0DrP6dMiMi0c9UqC6jr1DK6K9keI4biW7rHVs1tyq8YXKwQl8NP3kg9GIhjNKxE=w1280" style="width:10em;heigth:10em;"
    alt="GST Logo">
    <h1>Game Space Tracker</h1>
    <p>¡Bienvenido!<br>Aquí podrás administrar tus juegos favoritos para no perderte de nada.</p>
    <a href="/home" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Entrar</a>
  </div>

  <footer class="container-fluid bg-black text-light text-center py-3">
    <p>&copy; 2024 David González - Ricardo Gómez - Jose Vera</p>
  </footer>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
